title: Taiwan Kung Fu Exhibition 1988 Part 2
description:
Taiwan Kung Fu Exhibition 1988 Part 2

Demonstrations from various Kung Fu societies in Southern Taiwan 1988 

Language: Mandarin Chinese.


Some styles represented - 

Plum Boxing Mantis
Eight step Mantis
Pigua
Baji
Taiwan native Weapons  - Miao Dao (Sprout Sword)





Timings

Part 2 -    56:44
